CASE 
WHEN [exceptionMsg] LIKE '%(mserver5 still alive?)%' THEN 'Connection reset'
WHEN [exceptionMsg] LIKE '%SafeModeException%' THEN 'Out of memory'
WHEN [exceptionMsg] LIKE '%Failed to read row: 0, Connector%' THEN 'Connector error - read fail' 
WHEN [exceptionMsg] LIKE '%500 Internal Server Error%' THEN 'Server error'
WHEN [exceptionMsg] LIKE '%(Host is unavailable)%' THEN 'Failed to connect to data source'
WHEN [exceptionMsg] LIKE '%Error in the request from the data source.%' THEN 'Unable to import improperly formatted value'
WHEN [exceptionMsg] IS NULL THEN 'Successful build'
ELSE NULL END

SELECT o.trackingId AS [ActionID],o.timeStamp AS Date,o.[userId]
                     AS [User ID],o.[dashboardId]AS [Dashboard ID],tofloat(o.[loadTime]) AS
                     [Load Time],o.Action AS Action, o.category AS Category
FROM [usage] o

CASE
WHEN [source] IN ('ECM Sched','ECM Scheduler','ECMScheduler', 'Scheduler') THEN 'scheduled'
WHEN [source] = 'Api' THEN 'scheduled'
WHEN [source] = 'Manual' THEN 'manual'
WHEN [source] = 'NextECM' THEN 'manual'
WHEN [source] = 'PSM' THEN 'manual'
ELSE 'unknown'
END

CASE WHEN [action] = 'ecs_buildfail' THEN 'Fail'
WHEN [action] = 'ecs_buildsuccess' THEN 'Success'
ELSE NULL END

SELECT distinct o.DashboardID AS [Dashboard ID],
                o.dashboardPath AS [Dashboard Path],
                CASE WHEN StrParts(o.dashboardPath,'/',1) like '' THEN 'null'
                ELSE StrParts(o.dashboardPath,'/',1) END  AS [Dashboard Folder],
                o.dashboardTitle AS [Dashboard Name]
                FROM [usage] o
                WHERE o.[category] = 'Analytics'

SELECT [userId] AS [User ID],[User Name], Role, domain, CASE WHEN
                     IsNullOrEmpty([User Group])=TRUE then 'No Group' ELSE [User Group] END
                     AS[User Group]  
from
(SELECT o.[userId], o.[email] AS [User Name],
                     o.userRole AS Role, o.emailDomain AS Domain, strparts(o.userGroups,';',1) AS
                     [User Group]
FROM [usage] o
UNION

                     SELECT o.[userId], o.[email] AS [User Name],o.userRole  AS Role, o.emailDomain
                     AS Domain, strparts(o.userGroups,';',2) AS [User Group]
FROM [usage] o
WHERE
                     strparts(o.userGroups,';',2) !=''
UNION
SELECT o.[userId], o.[email] AS
                     [User Name],o.userRole  AS Role, o.emailDomain AS Domain,
                     strparts(o.userGroups,';',3) AS [User Group]
FROM [usage] o
WHERE
                     strparts(o.userGroups,';',3) !=''
) a

select cubeID, cubeName, startBuildTimeStamp as lastBuildDate, BuildId, 
countTables, ecbcntcols, countedProvidersCount, ecbinitialphysicalsize, 
tableMaxRows, tableTotalRows, tableCount, 
customMaxRows, customTotalRows, customCount,
customCodeMaxRows, customCodeTotalRows, customCodeCount,
totalRows_calc, totalTables_calc,
uniqueProviders
from [SummarizeBuild]
where [SummarizeBuild].[rank_builds] = 1 and [SummarizeBuild].[action] = 'ecs_buildsuccess'

SELECT [BuildId], [original], [connector] AS "connector"
FROM

	(
		SELECT [BuildId], [uniqueProviders] AS "original", CASE WHEN length(StrParts([uniqueProviders],',',1)) < 1 THEN [uniqueProviders] ELSE StrParts([uniqueProviders],',',1) END AS "connector"
		FROM [SummarizeBuild]
	
	UNION ALL 
	
		SELECT [BuildId], [uniqueProviders] AS "original", StrParts([uniqueProviders],',',2) AS "connector"
		FROM [SummarizeBuild]
	 
	UNION ALL 
	
		SELECT [BuildId], [uniqueProviders] AS "original", StrParts([uniqueProviders],',',3) AS "connector"
		FROM [SummarizeBuild]
	 
	UNION ALL 
	
		SELECT [BuildId], [uniqueProviders] AS "original", StrParts([uniqueProviders],',',4) AS "connector"
		FROM [SummarizeBuild]
	 
	UNION ALL 
	
		SELECT [BuildId], [uniqueProviders] AS "original", StrParts([uniqueProviders],',',5) AS "connector"
		FROM [SummarizeBuild]
		
	UNION ALL 
	
		SELECT [BuildId], [uniqueProviders] AS "original", StrParts([uniqueProviders],',',6) AS "connector"
		FROM [SummarizeBuild]
	 
	UNION ALL 
	
		SELECT [BuildId], [uniqueProviders] AS "original", StrParts([uniqueProviders],',',7) AS "connector"
		FROM [SummarizeBuild]
	 
	UNION ALL 
	
		SELECT [BuildId], [uniqueProviders] AS "original", StrParts([uniqueProviders],',',8) AS "connector"
		FROM [SummarizeBuild]

	) z
WHERE [connector] IS NOT NULL and [connector] <> ''

SELECT *
FROM (
SELECT *, 1 AS n, StrParts([uniqueProviders], ',', 1) AS source FROM [DimCubes]
UNION ALL
SELECT *, 2 AS n, StrParts([uniqueProviders], ',', 2) AS source FROM [DimCubes]  
UNION ALL
SELECT *, 3 AS n, StrParts([uniqueProviders], ',', 3) AS source FROM [DimCubes]
UNION ALL
SELECT *, 4 AS n, StrParts([uniqueProviders], ',', 4) AS source FROM [DimCubes]
UNION ALL
SELECT *, 5 AS n, StrParts([uniqueProviders], ',', 5) AS source FROM [DimCubes]
UNION ALL
SELECT *, 6 AS n, StrParts([uniqueProviders], ',', 6) AS source FROM [DimCubes]
) source_delimited
WHERE source != ''
